  <h1>Introduction</h1>

  <p>
    <strong>AI Stack FastAPI</strong> is a production-ready boilerplate for building
    RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) applications with complete vendor flexibility.
    It combines the speed of <strong>FastAPI</strong> with the modern frontend experience
    of <strong>Next.js 16</strong>.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 not-prose my-8">
